{"title":"Typera自动存储图片到七牛云","slug":"Typera自动存储图片到七牛云","date":"2022-05-12T08:22:43.000Z","updated":"2022-05-12T08:57:01.618Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Typera自动存储图片到七牛云.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"每次使用Typera都要整理文章的图片，专门放一个文件夹与文章一起放好，不然乱起来没法管理，甚至误删，得不偿失。其实typera本身就集成了PicGo的上传功能，这次设置一下，让他自己上传文件到云端，就不用费心思再组织图片了。","covers":["http://img.orangejuice.top/image/image-20220512163128725.png","http://img.orangejuice.top/image/image-20220512163957682.png","http://img.orangejuice.top/image/image-20220512165313314.png"],"content":"<p>每次使用Typera都要整理文章的图片，专门放一个文件夹与文章一起放好，不然乱起来没法管理，甚至误删，得不偿失。其实typera本身就集成了PicGo的上传功能，这次设置一下，让他自己上传文件到云端，就不用费心思再组织图片了。</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<h2 id=\"typera设置\"><a href=\"#typera设置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"typera设置\"></a>typera设置</h2><p>文件——&gt;偏好设置——&gt;图象</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://img.orangejuice.top/image/image-20220512163128725.png\" alt=\"image-20220512163128725\"></p>\n<ol>\n<li>选择上传图片，勾选框中的两个选项。</li>\n<li>选择PicGo-Core (command line)</li>\n<li>点击下载或更新（可能会下载失败，多试几次）。</li>\n<li>打开配置文件备用。</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"云存储设置\"><a href=\"#云存储设置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"云存储设置\"></a>云存储设置</h2><p>这里选用七牛云，每月免费10G容量，速度也可以，主要其他的图床也没怎么用过😃。公共图床用过<a href=\"https://imgtu.com/\" title=\"\" target=\"\">路过图床</a> ，其实也挺好用的，但是安全性就不知道了。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>七牛云首先注册账号，然后申请对象存储，新建空间。</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"http://img.orangejuice.top/image/image-20220512163957682.png\" alt=\"image-20220512163957682\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p> 你的空间名和存储区域将会被用到</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>给你的空间绑定域名，你需要先购买域名！</li>\n<li>至于SSL，https 的流量是不计入免费套餐的，如果你需要就去配置一下。</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"picGo配置\"><a href=\"#picGo配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"picGo配置\"></a>picGo配置</h2><p>进入七牛云的密钥管理：</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://img.orangejuice.top/image/image-20220512165313314.png\" alt=\"image-20220512165313314\"></p>\n<p>查看你的AK和SK。</p>\n<p>回到typera第四步打开的配置文件，补充以下内容</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight json\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"punctuation\">&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">&quot;picBed&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"punctuation\">&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"attr\">&quot;uploader&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;qiniu&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"attr\">&quot;qiniu&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"punctuation\">&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"attr\">&quot;accessKey&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;****************************************&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"comment\">//AK</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"attr\">&quot;secretKey&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;****************************************&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"comment\">//SK</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"attr\">&quot;bucket&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;picture&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"comment\">// 存储空间名</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"attr\">&quot;url&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;你的域名&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"comment\">// 自定义域名</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"attr\">&quot;area&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span>  <span class=\"string\">&quot;z0&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"comment\">// 存储区域编号，华东z0 华北z1 华南z2 北美z3 东南亚z4</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"attr\">&quot;options&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"comment\">// 网址后缀，比如？abc</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"attr\">&quot;path&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;img/&quot;</span> <span class=\"comment\">// 自定义存储路径，比如 img/</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"punctuation\">&#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"punctuation\">&#125;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">&quot;picgoPlugins&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"punctuation\">&#123;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">&#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"punctuation\">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<hr>\n<p>所有配置完成，直接粘贴图片进typera，你会惊喜的发现图片还是本地地址！</p>\n<p>不要急，图片上会显示上传，片刻之后图片地址就会显示你配置的域名了。</p>\n","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"七牛云","slug":"七牛云","count":1,"path":"api/tags/七牛云.json"},{"name":"typera","slug":"typera","count":1,"path":"api/tags/typera.json"}]}